<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="jn0042a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="jn0" href="#jn0042">JN0: </a>  <a href="../../FF/unbs/jn0all.htm#jn0042a"> (I.A) 42(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <p class="epiplace">[Dublin: in the house in <br>Glengariff Parade: evening] </p> <p class="epidial">Mrs Joyce &mdash; (<i>crimson, trembling, appears at the <br>parlour door</i>)&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. Jim! </p> <p class="epidial">Joyce &mdash; (<i>at the piano</i>)&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. Yes? </p> <p class="epidial">Mrs Joyce &mdash; Do you know anything about the <br>body?&nbsp;.&nbsp;. What ought I do?&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. There&apos;s <br>some matter coming away from <br>the hole in Georgie&apos;s stomach&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. <br>Did you ever hear of that happening? </p> <p class="epidial">Joyce &mdash; (<i>surprised</i>)&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. I don&apos;t know&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. </p> <p class="epidial">Mrs Joyce &mdash; Ought I send for the doctor, do you <br<think? </p> <p class="epidial">Joyce &mdash; I don&apos;t know&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. What hole? </p> <p class="epidial">Mrs Joyce &mdash; (<i>impatient</i>)&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. The hole we all have <br>.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;. here (<i>points</i>) </p> <p class="epidial">Joyce &mdash; (<i>stands up</i>) </p></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="jn0042a"><li>Stephen Hero <a href="../../ulex/ap/lexsh.htm#jn0042a">ED</a> </li><li><ms href="#jn0042a">MS Harvard 762-3</ms> </li><li>JJA 8:539,41 </li><li><a name="sh.1" href="../udra/shda.htm#sh11d">Usage</a> </li><li><a href="../../ulex/ap/sh11d.htm#jn0042a">Draft: sh.1</a></li> </ul><mm class="note">Note: Silverman/La Hune no. XVII. Relating to the death of Joyce&apos;s brother Georgie in March 1902, this epiphany forms the basis for a scene in <cite>Stephen Hero</cite> (see <a href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.59181/page/n165/mode/2up" target="_blank">page 168 of the 1956 Jonathan Cape edition</a>).</mm> </dd></dl>
